* This version of the ReferenceSequence resource only considers the related reference sequence associations between amino acid and transcript reference sequences. This has constrained the scope of codes in the [value set](/allele/implementation/value_set_list/reference_sequence_relationship_type.html) for the ReferenceSequence.Related.relatedType attribute. 


